        <p class="feature__top-lead--l">「The Flex Arm」</p>
        <p class="feature__top-lead">
          The Flex Arm is an air balancer with a wide operating range that supports a rated payload of 50 kg.<br>
          It can be mounted on columns or ceilings, allowing for flexible adaptation to sites with low ceilings or limited floor space.<br>
          It can be adapted to sites where installing assisting devices was previously difficult, contributing to improved work efficiency and workplace enhancement.
        </p>
