        <!-- POINT01 -->
        <div class="feature__article" id="point01">
          <div class="feature__box" id="box01">
            <h3 class="feature__box-title-wrap">
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--s">POINT</span>
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--l">01</span>
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--m">Simple</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="feature__box-lead">Simple Structure & Easy Operation</p>
          </div>
          <p class="feature__point-txt">With its intuitive structure, anyone can handle it right away. No complex operations or adjustments are required.</p>
  
          <ul class="common-section__list">
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">Easy Transport of Heavy Objects</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">Powered by compressed air, you can work while holding heavy objects of up to 50 kg (including attachment weight) with light operation.</p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image01">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_01.png" alt="軽い操作性">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">Workpiece Weight Detection System</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">
                  The workpiece weight detection system can detect the weight of any workpiece within the payload capacity.<br>
                  It can easily balance multiple workpieces with different weights, allowing anyone to work smoothly.
                </p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image02">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_02.png" alt="水平アームと垂直ガイド">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">
                Simple Structure for<br>
                Easy Maintenance
              </h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">The simple structure using an air cylinder allows for easy maintenance and provides stable operation.</p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image03">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_03.png" alt="上下任意位置でバランス">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

