              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--l">02</span>
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--m">Wide</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="feature__box-lead">Wide Operating Range, Minimal Height</p>
          </div>
          <p class="feature__point-txt">It has a wide range of motion and a low overall height compared to the stroke, allowing it to flexibly handle even in small spaces.</p>
  
          <ul class="common-section__list">
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">Wide Operating Range</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">With a wide operating range of a 2.5 m turning radius and a 1.5 m vertical stroke, a single unit can cover an extensive work area.</p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image04">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_04.jpeg" alt="Wide Operating Range">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">Wide 320° Rotation Range</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">
                  The arm can rotate up to 320°, flexibly adapting to a wide work area.<br>
                  It is also possible to apply a rotation restriction at any position, allowing for operation that considers safety and workability.
                </p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image05">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_05.jpeg" alt="Wide 320° Rotation Range">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">Can Be Installed Even in Low-Ceiling Areas</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">
                  With a low overall height of 2.5 m, it can be installed without issue even in sites with low ceilings.<br>
                  *Height varies depending on the specifications.
                </p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image06">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_06.jpg" alt="Can Be Installed Even in Low-Ceiling Areas">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- POINT03 -->
        <div class="feature__article" id="point03">
          <div class="feature__box" id="box03">
            <h3 class="feature__box-title-wrap">
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--s">POINT</span>
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--l">03</span>
              <span class="feature__box-text feature__box-text--m">Safety</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="feature__box-lead">Safe for Anyone to Use</p>
          </div>
          <p class="feature__point-txt">With a design that emphasizes safety, even first-time users can use it with peace of mind.</p>
  
          <ul class="common-section__list">
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">All-Air Specification</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">Because it is an all-air specification that does not require a power source, it can be used safely even in sites where explosion-proofing is required.</p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image07">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_07.jpg" alt="It also contributes to reducing risks at the worksite.">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">
                Drop Prevention<br>
                When Air is Shut Off
              </h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">Even if the air supply is cut off, the shut-off valve activates and the arm stops in place. This prevents heavy objects from falling and ensures safety.</p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image08">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_08.jpg" alt="Because it is an all-air specification that does not require a power source, it can be used safely even in sites where explosion-proofing is required.">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="common-section__card">
              <h4 class="common-section__card-title">Drop Prevention Function</h4>
              <div class="common-section__card-box">
                <p data-mh="listTxt01" class="common-section__card-text">
                  The vacuum specification attachment is equipped with a safety function to prevent accidental button presses due to incorrect operation.<br>
                  Even in the event of an incorrect operation, it prevents heavy objects from falling and enhances work safety.
                </p>
                <div class="common-section__card-image  --image09">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_list_img_09.png" alt="Drop Prevention Function">
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
  
