    <section id="line-up" class="line-up">
      <div class="l-inner">
        <h2 class="line-up__title">Options</h2>
        <p class="line-up__sub-title">Four Types of Installation Methods</p>
        <p class="line-up__lead">
          The Flex Arm allows you to choose from mainly the following four installation methods.<br>
          Flexible installation is possible to match the site's environment and needs.
        </p>
        <div class="line-up__block">
          <div class="line-up__image-block line-up__img-block--small --image01">
            <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_line_up_img_01.png" alt="サイズL　低荷重モデル">
          </div>
          <div class="line-up__text-block">
            <h3 class="line-up__block-title">Floor-mounted Fixed</h3>
            <p class="line-up__block-text">
              Used by fixing it to the floor with anchors.<br>
              This is the most adopted specification, optimal for locations where the work area is fixed and installation on the floor is possible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="line-up__block">
          <div class="line-up__image-block line-up__img-block--small --image02">
            <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_line_up_img_02.png" alt="サイズH　高荷重モデル">
          </div>
          <div class="line-up__text-block">
            <h3 class="line-up__block-title">Floor-mounted Pallet</h3>
            <p class="line-up__block-text">
              During installation, it is fixed to the floor with angles or similar items.<br>
              This specification is optimal when it will be used in multiple locations or if there is a possibility of changing the installation location in the future.<br>
              We assume the use of a forklift for moving it,<br>
              but please consult with us if you are considering other moving methods.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="line-up__block">
          <div class="line-up__image-block line-up__img-block--small --image03">
            <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_line_up_img_03.png" alt="サイズH　高荷重モデル">
          </div>
          <div class="line-up__text-block">
            <h3 class="line-up__block-title">Column-mounted</h3>
            <p class="line-up__block-text">
              This specification allows installation if there is a nearby column, even when installation space on the floor cannot be secured.<br>
              Since it leaves the floor area clear, it does not obstruct work flow lines, enabling an efficient layout.<br>
              *Column strength verification is required for installation.
            </p>
            <div class="line-up__block-movie common-movie--small">
              <div class="common-movie-wrap">
                <a data-target="modal01" class="common__js_modal_open" href="">
                  <img src="../assets/images/feature/movie_thumb_02.jpg" alt="サムネイル">
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="line-up__block">
          <div class="line-up__image-block line-up__img-block--small --image04">
            <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_line_up_img_04.png" alt="サイズH　高荷重モデル">
          </div>
          <div class="line-up__text-block">
            <h3 class="line-up__block-title">Ceiling-mounted</h3>
            <p class="line-up__block-text">
              This is a method of fixing it to the ceiling when there is no installation space on the floor.<br>
              If installation is difficult due to the ceiling's height, strength, or structure, flexible solutions such as installing a scaffold or mounting to a rail system are also possible.<br>
              *Ceiling strength verification is required for installation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="line-up__block line-up__block--margin-large">
          <div class="line-up__image-block line-up__img-block--small --image05">
            <img src="../assets/images/feature/feature_line_up_img_05.png" alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="line-up__text-block">
            <h3 class="line-up__block-title">Arm Tip Attachments</h3>
            <p class="line-up__block-text">
              The tip of the Flex Arm is equipped with a suspension hook as standard.<br>
              By attaching various attachments to the suspension hook, it can handle a variety of workpieces.<br>
              Customization according to the customer's application is also possible.
            </p>
